xboxdrv-linux: xboxdrv-linux (Userspace Xbox/Xbox360 USB Gamepad Driver for Linux)
xboxdrv-linux:
xboxdrv-linux: Xboxdrv is a Xbox/Xbox360 gamepad driver for Linux that works in
xboxdrv-linux: userspace. It is an alternative to the xpad kernel driver and has
xboxdrv-linux: support for Xbox1 gamepads, Xbox360 USB gamepads and Xbox360 wireless
xboxdrv-linux: gamepads, both first and third party.
xboxdrv-linux:
xboxdrv-linux: Homepage: http://pingus.seul.org/~grumbel/xboxdrv/
